        <item>
            <title>掌上遊戲機操控模組有得換！更多「三代」AYANEO 細節公佈</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/03/more-details-announce-on-ayaneo-3-with-changable-joystick-module/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=more-details-announce-on-ayaneo-3-with-changable-joystick-module</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/03/more-details-announce-on-ayaneo-3-with-changable-joystick-module/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Edward]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 03:00:17 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AYANEO]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AYANEO 3]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1284852</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>去年不少廠商都紛紛推出自家採用 Windows 11 OS 的掌上遊戲機，而且各出奇謀，競爭十分激烈，而這個新市場鬥爭相信去到今年將會持續。AYANEO 就率先宣佈將會推出第三代的旗艦級掌上遊戲機，最突破是它擁有可更換手製模組的設計，令大家可按玩哪類型的遊戲而使用合適操控，相信會令打機手感直線提升。</p><p>今次發佈的 AYANEO 3，設有黑、白兩色設計，配置上用家可選擇 AMD Ryzen 7 8840U 或 AMD Ryzen AI 9 HX 370 版本，而內建的 7 吋 1080p 熒幕，亦有支援 120Hz 更新率的 LCD 或支援 144Hz 更新率的 OLED 選擇。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284855" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_002-694x362.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="362" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_002-694x362.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_002.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284856" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_014-694x362.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="362" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_014-694x362.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_014.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲AYANEO 3 設有黑、白兩色設計。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284857" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_017-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_017-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_017.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284858" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_016-694x475.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="475" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_016-694x475.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_016.jpg 1276w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲配置上用家可選擇 AMD Ryzen 7 8840U 或 AMD Ryzen AI 9 HX 370 版本，而內建的 7 吋 1080p 熒幕，亦有支援 120Hz 更新率的 LCD 或支援 144Hz 更新率的 OLED 選擇。</p><p>不過 AYANEO 3 最突破的設計，肯定是它的一對可替換兼可自定義擺位的手製模組。有玩開掌上遊戲機的用家應該都會感受到，現今市場上很難有一部掌上遊戲機玩任何遊戲也有一流的操控手感，而 AYANEO 3 就設有 3 對可供替換的手製模組，無論大家是想用雙蘑菇 + 方向盤 + ABXY 鍵玩冒險遊戲，還是要用到觸控板玩傳統策略遊戲，甚或要用到 ABCXYZ 亦個動作鍵玩格鬥類遊戲（例如：拳王），它都有相對應的模組配置，基本上用家只需放入合適模組再啟動遊戲即可。而且不只模組可以自設，就連上下位置也可調轉插入，以適應不同手形或操控習慣的用家，而調轉後的按鍵亦可取出並以適當方向裝回模組上，令調轉模組插入機身時，按鍵上顯示的文字不會上下調轉，設計十分體貼。可以説的是，在設計上，AYANEO 3 配合這個全新可替換的手製模組，是現時掌上遊戲機界最體貼用家操控需要的機款。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284859" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_005-694x362.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="362" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_005-694x362.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_005.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲AYANEO 3 最突破的設計，肯定是這個可替換的手製模組。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284860" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_010-694x363.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="363" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_010-694x363.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_010.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲它設有 3 對手製模組供用家按不同遊戲選用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284861" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_011-694x364.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="364" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_011-694x364.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_011.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲模組不但可自由替換，亦可上下調轉，而按鍵亦可取出並按合適方向裝回，讓不同操控習慣的用家，也可以最舒適的方式打機。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284862" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_015-694x365.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="365" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_015-694x365.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_015.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲模組亦會按機身顏色而有不同設計，像白機就會配置白色手製模組。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284863" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_006-694x364.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="364" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_006-694x364.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_006.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至於接駁模組的方法，官方暫時未有透露，但筆者從影片觀察估計應是採用磁吸模式，這樣拆出或裝上模組會是最方便。</p><p>不過現時 AYANEO 3 仍在開發階段，所以未有更多細節公佈，定價、推出日期亦有待確認。有興趣的讀者可以瀏覽以下官方介紹片看看 AYANEO 3 的設計有多大突破。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_88017"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/_r7L1_0C6EE?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>來源：<a href="https://www.ayaneo.com/product/AYANEO-3">AYANEO</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/01/03/more-details-announce-on-ayaneo-3-with-changable-joystick-module/fun-tech/">掌上遊戲機操控模組有得換！更多「三代」AYANEO 細節公佈</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
